1 CONC From an Appanoose County newspaper:
1 CONT
1 CONT "Funeral services were conducted from Fairview Church at 2 o'clock Sunday afternoon for the late Daniel I. Gladfelder, Rev. J.W. Zerbe officiating.
1 CONT
1 CONT Daniel I. Gladfelder, son of John and Phoebe Gladfelder, was born June 7, 1868.  He grew to manhood in tis vicinity but has resided in Kansas City, Kansas, for the past 30 years where he passed away Thursday, Oct. 20, 1932, at the age of 64 years
1 CONC , 4 months and 13 days.  He was preceded in death by his father, mother and two sisters and is survived by the following brothers and sisters: Mrs. G.R. Duff, Mr. M.G. Smith, David, Delbert and Charles Gladfelder and a number of other relatives an
1 CONC d friends."
1 CONT
