1 CONC o was 16.  The two households are only about 15 miles apart, and the two census pages were dated 2 July 1860 (Barnett Twp, DeWitt Co) and 25 July 1860 (Mt Pulaski, Logan Co).  It's possible that Harrison and "Wm H" are the same person, in which ca
1 CONC se Harrison's full name is William Harrison Meachum.
